<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="O" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Ought2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Ought,</orth> vb. 1) owed: <cit><quote>you o. him a thousand pound,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.152" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 3, 152</bibl></cit> (Mrs Quickly's speech).<lb />2) to be bound in duty; should necessarily; followed by an inf. with <cit><quote>to:</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.103" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 1, 103</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mm 2.1.56" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. II, 1, 56</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 2.3.202" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 3, 202</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 3.3.87" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 87</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.1.30" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 1, 30</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.1.30" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 1, 30</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.4.7" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 4, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 5.303" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. V, 303</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 5.3.110" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 V, 3, 110</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.2.139" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 2, 139</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.6.58" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 6, 58</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.1.28" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 1, 28</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.7.54" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 7, 54</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.7.44" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C IV, 7, 44</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 2.2.131" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 II, 2, 131</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.3.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 3, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 2.1.270" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. II, 1, 270</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 5.3.324" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. V, 3, 324</bibl>. <emph>I o. so</emph> (viz to answer) <bibl n="shak. cor 3.3.62" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. III, 3, 62</bibl>. Inf. without <emph>to</emph>: <cit><quote>you o. not walk without the sign of your profession,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jc 1.1.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. I, 1, 3</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>